{"tid":2066281,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿迪達：15歲就被哥帥影響","createTime":"2020-06-16T07:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:47:21.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"826fdd1186179f20bd5d7ade44b14601166f5890","tid":2066281,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmwMwVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmwMwVO.jpg&h=0e0b6edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿迪達：15歲就被哥帥影響<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】英超周三重啟，阿仙奴作客曼城。兵工廠領隊阿迪達直言，被前「上司」、藍月主帥哥迪奧拿影響極深。<br />\n<br />\n阿迪達（Mikel Arteta）在掛靴後便加入曼城，擔任主帥哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）的副手。3年多後，他於去年12月20日回歸阿仙奴坐正，今場是他首次以領隊身份，跟哥帥打對台。 「在我15歲的時候，我在巴塞隆拿認識了哥迪奧拿，他自此一直影響著我。」阿迪達說。「在執教生涯及私人生活，他對我的影響都很大。他的價值觀，他對待我的態度，他處理職球員的方法，全都是無與倫比的。」 阿迪達坦言從哥帥身上學習良多：「我們一起度過了一些非常神奇的時刻，以及十分困難的關口。所有在他身邊的經驗都是令人難以置信的。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/阿迪達-15歲就被哥帥影響-234611700.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E9%98%BF%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%94-15%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%93%A5%E5%B8%A5%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-234611700.html&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f1754724\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/阿迪達-15歲就被哥帥影響-234611700.html</a></span>"},{"pid":"5d523abb96ff4d4180bec3f417950b4b6ad96ac8","tid":2066281,"uid":283189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a55df8ce5b64e95feb102c43b3e7a0025f7c9c","tid":2066281,"uid":283189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"bot係曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d097a062ddf46d1f6a7225c03219c505aed86d","tid":2066281,"uid":15009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"非財經台無